videos.description: In the final seconds of Kansas' 10-point win over West Virginia, Perry Ellis gets the ball in transition and finishes with a one-handed jam.
videos.headline: Ellis dunks Kansas to Big 12 title

videos.description: Kansas coach Bill Self praises Devonte' Graham saying his confidence remained high, adding that his performance was "unreal." Graham then turns the praise back on his teammates saying he couldn't have done it without his guys.
videos.headline: Self, Graham thrilled to be Big 12 Champs
